snippet.title: HITMAN - Elusive Targets: The Sensation Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/hitman-ps4/


The fourth Elusive Target has arrived.  
Make sure you're ready. There are no second chances.  

Elusive Targets will appear for a limited time only.  They can only ever be killed once.  Intel will be limited.  Plan carefully.  If you die during the mission…  That is it.  
When time runs out, they are gone for good.  DON’T MISS OUT  

For more information on the game and Elusive Targets:
https://hitman.com/en-us/news/hitman-live-component

Rated Mature: Blood, Drug Reference, Intense Violence, Strong Language, Suggestive Themes
